<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 14:06:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>不方便的背景：巴勒斯坦人因为犹太人而屠杀犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</link><description>坚持认为加沙周边以色列社区 1,300 多人被谋杀只是有政治背景，就是故意忽视哈马斯、真主党、法国和巴基斯坦伊斯兰主义者谋杀犹太人与匹兹堡枪击案之间的联系</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 13:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>布鲁克林篮网队与拉阿纳纳马卡比队的 NBA 季前赛变成了对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</link><description>在哈马斯周六对以色列平民进行屠杀之后，与以色列有关的一切都不再一样了——包括周四以色列球队与美国 NBA 对手之间的例行篮球比赛</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者记录在西岸近距离射杀巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-documented-shooting-palestinian-at-point-blank-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-28e3-d450-a3af-69ffcb950000</link><description>该事件发生在希伯伦以南的巴勒斯坦阿图瓦尼村附近。镜头中还可以看到一名以色列国防军士兵站在定居者附近的背景中</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:23:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-documented-shooting-palestinian-at-point-blank-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-28e3-d450-a3af-69ffcb950000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的品牌：没有责任，没有责任，没有悔恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</link><description>周四，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡组建了“临时战时内阁”，将他的零责任、始终分担责任的态度提升到了一个新的水平。在任何其他情况下，这都是正确的做法——对他来说，这只是确保加沙战争失败的责任归咎于其他人的另一种方式</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质是以色列的致命弱点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</link><description>被哈马斯在加沙绑架的以色列人（其中包括妇女、儿童、婴儿和老人）的视频和图像令人痛苦，触动了以色列政体最柔软、最脆弱的弱点</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新的哈马斯-加沙概念注定会失败，就像上一个概念一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</link><description>以色列对待哈马斯的态度是错误的，将其视为一个政治组织，可以通过经济激励来影响其取得成果。像对待伊斯兰国一样对哈马斯发动战争是一个谬论，它掩盖了加沙地带冲突后控制问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国和欧洲的支持下，以色列正在摧毁加沙。它必须考虑后天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</link><description>哈马斯的恐怖袭击和以色列受害者的数量令人难以想象。与此同时，加沙人面临的只有地狱和毁灭。一旦复仇的欲望稍稍消退，我们必须要问：加沙将会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带的起源及其周围的以色列社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</link><description>加沙汹涌的仇恨之海正是这些以色列社区本应“笼罩”的</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军监测以色列-加沙边境的气球在哈马斯袭击前几周破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</link><description>以色列军队上周未能修复边境监控技术；目前正在研究哈马斯破坏气球的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</guid></item><item><title>研究揭示了中东史前暴力的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</link><description>对 14,000 至 2,400 年前的 3,500 具骨骼的分析发现了暴力历史中的细微差别。有时可以包容</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</guid></item><item><title>这就是乌克兰与以色列站在一起的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</link><description>针对以色列的可怕恐怖袭击引起了乌克兰人的共鸣。火箭、酷刑和谋杀、绑架儿童——我们太了解这个剧本了。但我们的悲剧的相似之处并非偶然</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙和黎巴嫩之间行走，等待真主党的下一步行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/dogged-by-nightmares-israel-walks-a-thin-line-between-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-255b-d680-af9b-27dfe0390000</link><description>以色列军队必须决定是应该集中在一条战线还是两条战线上 ■ 导致最终失败的误解和情报错误 ■ 现在指责那些对恐怖事件负责的人还为时过早 ■ 违反与人民的契约</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 04:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/dogged-by-nightmares-israel-walks-a-thin-line-between-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-255b-d680-af9b-27dfe0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列：一个饱受创伤、失去政府的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-a-country-in-trauma-bereft-of-government/0000018b-2579-d3fc-a3bf-bffd6baa0000</link><description>以色列人现在有一种倒置的无政府状态，这激发了整个国家的希望 ■ 对于内塔尼亚胡来说，分裂不是一个错误，而是一个特征</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 03:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-a-country-in-trauma-bereft-of-government/0000018b-2579-d3fc-a3bf-bffd6baa0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹在以色列北部上空被拦截；美国国防部长称哈马斯“比伊斯兰国更糟糕”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-live/israels-war-on-hamas-enters-day-7-un-says-over-423-000-palestinians-in-gaza-displaced/0000018b-2675-d1bc-a58b-6ff7c4290000</link><description>超过 120 名死者连夜抵达加沙医院 ■ 人权观察称以色列在黎巴嫩加沙使用白磷 ■ 哈马斯袭击后，以色列发布被杀儿童的照片以争取支持 ■ 自周六以来，已有 1,200 多名以色列人被杀 ■ 1,799 名巴勒斯坦人巴勒斯坦卫生部称，自战争爆发以来加沙已有人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 02:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-live/israels-war-on-hamas-enters-day-7-un-says-over-423-000-palestinians-in-gaza-displaced/0000018b-2675-d1bc-a58b-6ff7c4290000</guid></item><item><title>反对对加沙进行集体惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/no-to-collective-punishment-against-gaza/0000018b-254d-dd34-afdf-f5cfb9f00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 01:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/no-to-collective-punishment-against-gaza/0000018b-254d-dd34-afdf-f5cfb9f00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的不归路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-point-of-no-return/0000018b-254d-d3fc-a3bf-bfedb7e00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 01:26:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-point-of-no-return/0000018b-254d-d3fc-a3bf-bfedb7e00000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯以色列小镇社区凶杀潮中男子被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-israeli-town-amid-community-homicide-wave/0000018b-264a-de5b-a59f-ee6b77430000</link><description>据《国土报》统计，今年以色列阿拉伯社区已有 197 人被杀，而 2022 年全年这一数字为 112 人</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 00:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-israeli-town-amid-community-homicide-wave/0000018b-264a-de5b-a59f-ee6b77430000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的话必须成为以色列的道德指